Titolo: The Infectious Madness of Doctor Dekker

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: The Infectious Madness of Doctor Dekker is a FMV murder mystery adventure video game developed by D'avekki Studios and written by Tim Cowles and Lynda Cowles. You play as a psychiatrist, trying to solve a murder whilst treating the patients of the recently deceased Doctor Dekker. The game was initially released on Steam for Microsoft Windows and macOS before being published on consoles by British game publishing studio, Wales Interactive.Another game, by the same creators The Shapeshifting Detective was released in the following year.